title: [Abandoned Homestead, Sunflowers]
description: The path leads through a field of sunflowers.  The irregular spacing of the rows of sunflowers suggest they had once been planted for harvesting but have begun to grow wild.  The large heads of the flowers are closed in the moonlight.

The path leads through a field of sunflowers.  The irregular spacing of the rows of sunflowers suggest they had once been planted for harvesting but have begun to grow wild.  The large yellow heads of the flowers are all turned to face the sun.
